<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Scenic Acres</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">The Scenic Acres Real Estate is flanked by the Stoney Trail, Crowchild Trail and the Nose Hill Drive on the west, north and south and east boundaries respectively. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Located at a distance of around 14km from the central downtown Calgary, Scenic Acres lies between the Crowchild Trail and Bow River.</p>
            <p class="par-xl">Given the fact that it is largely an upscale neighborhood, Scenic Acres homes for sale typically comprise of single family homes.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Schools in Scenic Acres include Monsignor Doyle Elementary School, St. Francis, St. Vincent de Paul, Belvedere Park Elementary and so on.</p>
        </div>
